==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: embezzled
<hw>embezzled</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>taken for one's own
use in violation of a trust; -- of money; <as>as, the banker absconded
with <ex>embezzled</ex> payroll; the <ex>embezzled</ex> funds amounted
to millions of dollars</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> misappropriated.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Embezzlement</ent>⟦br⟧
